ygData.messageBody:
Hi guys. AS i am now bored of reading about twinking...i thought i would pose a question out to my higher level brothers and sisters. This weekend, i competed in a guild scavenger hunt and won. My prize was a Staff of Writhing and a Crested Helm. My level is only 10 right now and i know this is kinda expensive/rare stuff, especially the helm. My question is what do you think i should trade for? Because i have no clue. Following is a list of my equipment that i already have:

Foreman Tunic (borrowed)
cloth sandals
mammoth leggings (borrowed)
cloth cape
cloth arms
serp bracer (borrowed), mesh bracelet
Jagged band ( borrowed )
Band of flesh
mesh neck
cloth cape
Wu's Gauntlets
cloth shoulders
Splitpaw mask

I guess that is about it....i have a friend who is going to make me cured silk all i have to do is get the heady kiolas. Hopefully you guys can lead me in the right direction. Thanks.

Muhammed
10th level brother of the Ashen order
Xegony
